{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd289d78d4","title":"鹰厦铁路死伤民工一千多人","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"becc729eba","index":0,"year":1956,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"bd289d78d4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"42f2361d51","name":"刘葵华"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d8293119af","type":"title","text":"鹰厦铁路死伤民工一千多人","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd289d78d4"},{"id":"2b697fb1a0","type":"authors","text":"刘葵华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd289d78d4"},{"id":"cfcd8e1191","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社福州6日讯：据福建省支前委员会调查，从今年1月至4月，修建鹰厦铁路的民工因工伤事故而死亡的已达四十一人，重伤一百三十七人，轻伤一千三百多人。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd289d78d4"},{"id":"4c379bfdd9","type":"paragraph","text":"造成伤亡事故的主要原因是：领导施工的干部对安全生产重视不够，在各个施工环节中缺乏对民工进行安全教育。今年前四个月工伤死亡的四十一人中，有三十八人因安全施工常识不足，在爆破、开挖土石方和搬运等施工活动中死亡的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd289d78d4"},{"id":"2b1eb65f01","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据1956年6月6日新华社《内部参考》。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd289d78d4"}],"page":{"id":"a97a64db6f","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd289d78d4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}